# Shared agent skills directory.
#
# `.claude/skills` and `.cursor/skills` are symlinks to this directory, so both
# coding agents see the same skills. The gitbutler skill is installed here as
# `ai/skills/gitbutler` by the but.nix dev shell on shell entry; it is a symlink
# into the Nix store and is gitignored (see /.gitignore).
